Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被無視的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看不起的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無家可歸 只能在街頭徬徨時腳底的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服被切得破碎不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這種心如刀絞的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如自己的身體被切碎比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣 反而要好得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把真綯從Black★Rock Shooter體內救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果無法實現這個目標的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不願意親手殺死真綯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這事我絕對不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是由宇的思念體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要思念體消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇現在所懷抱的痛苦就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記痛苦的由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法繼續留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想回到現實裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓妳這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為由宇是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑 一點光線也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀕臨崩塌的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Black★Rock Shooter的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是妳的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black★Rock Shooter
