Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要做那種事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是消失了 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不得不回到現實裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…那可是孤單一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已經無處可歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤單一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯可是想要拯救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拯救由宇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把一切都推給了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的痛苦 煩惱 迷茫推給了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是這樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想傷害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是由宇 黃泉 還是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要受傷 自己好好的受一次傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 想要受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 不受傷的話就無法看到各種世界了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我想要見證 目不轉睛的直視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉的橙色也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清風的粉紅也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的蔚藍也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦朧的紫色也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有噴薄而出的火紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是伴隨著疼痛的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要親眼去見證這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭不知不覺就會痊癒的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望自己受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就讓妳受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們不同 妳們的傷可不會那麼容易就痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不用那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我才不會用這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不想傷害其他任何人 只希望自己受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 傷害他人的…痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要不傷害他人 只有自己受傷什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅受到這麼一點傷害就無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去傷害他人什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩的記憶也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的天空！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 為了見到各式各樣的色彩我要飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而為了飛翔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡幡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會忘記呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為放不下篝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道和別人成為朋友的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡真綯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想把痛苦和煩惱與別人連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻有十分重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對我們而言 那些十分重要的孩子們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了重要的我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我喜歡黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕受傷也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 也想要連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black★Rock Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要傷害妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害妳 傷害妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和妳連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法和現實戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實的敵人 實在太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小沙耶在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有真綯在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定能交到很多朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 由宇妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界合為一體了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像世界能夠合為一體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈也是可以合而為一的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會喜歡上我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…由宇的思念體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有感情 為由宇而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不僅僅如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只會依靠本能行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正因為如此 所以才無法為討厭的他人而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最喜歡妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要保護妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想看見妳們哭泣的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才一直戰鬥至今啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…最喜歡妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對自己最喜歡的由宇撒謊的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現實是一個非常美妙的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真綯告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴了我那個世界的美妙之處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起回家的歸途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴了我什麼叫做稍縱即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴了我在回家路上吃得冰淇淋的那份甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴了我和朋友一起觀賞的夕陽的那份鮮紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠…永遠都是朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇妳個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black★Rock Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最喜歡妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事情想告訴真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…比如想要道歉的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳那麼痛苦 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也願意接受痛楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我們一起好好的承受這份痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 就像小孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界擁有各種色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炫目的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好難得 居然自己起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快點吃完 準備上學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是紘他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污穢的色彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:19.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的色彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:22.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有悲傷的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:23.61,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.02,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かのようになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.02,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要變得和某人一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.99,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどなれるはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.99,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又明白無法實現這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是只有美麗的色彩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.79,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いじけるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.79,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果為此垂頭喪氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:47.05,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心の中にいるもう一人の自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:47.05,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}存在於心中的另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.52,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}教えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.52,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}會告訴我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:20:00.60,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あるがままなんかじゃきっといられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:20:00.60,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一成不變畏縮不前的話一定會被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算如此 果然這個世界還是很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:07.33,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もがみんな悩んでもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:07.33,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論是誰 大家都背負著苦惱而掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:14.42,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}弱音吐いたり 愚痴ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:14.42,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}偶爾示弱 偶爾牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有各種事 各種色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:21.38,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そうやって毎日を過ごしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:21.38,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣度過了每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.14,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}傷つけられることに慣れた僕らは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.14,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於習慣受傷的我們已然知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算如此 我們…也會一一接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:34.97,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}優しさとか思いだけじゃ生きて行けないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:34.97,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只靠溫柔的願望無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:41.33,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど自分らしくありたいと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:41.33,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是希望可以保持自我的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受一切 然後各自長大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:49.70,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつだって 僕ら歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:49.70,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論何時 我們都會一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…逐漸長大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:06.37,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:12.23,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あとどれだけ叫べばいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:12.23,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}之後究竟要嘶喊多久才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:18.07,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あとどれだけ泣けばいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:18.07,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}之後究竟要哭泣多久才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:24.38,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もうやめて わたしはもう走れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:24.38,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}快停下吧 我已經無法再奔跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:29.62,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか夢見た世界が閉じる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:29.62,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不知何時夢中的世界早已關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:40.29,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真っ暗で明かりもない 崩れかけたこの道で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:40.29,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一片漆黑不見光明 在這條瀕臨崩塌的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:51.78,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あるはずもないあの時の希望が見えた気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:51.78,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻好像看見了那個時候不可能存在的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:52.88,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:52.88,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:58.29,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ブラック★ロックシューター　懐かしい記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:58.29,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Black★Rock Shooter 令人懷念的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:04.39,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ楽しかったあの頃を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:04.39,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}尚且無憂無慮的那時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:09.81,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ブラック★ロックシューター　でも動けないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:09.81,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Black★Rock Shooter 但是無法動彈喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:15.08,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇を駆ける星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:15.08,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向著在黑暗中奔走的流星祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:20.78,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう一度だけ走るから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:20.78,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}希望能夠再一次向前奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷抱著痛楚和傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這個世界裡 繼續戰鬥